==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mogen David
<hw>Mogen David</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hebrew, shield of
David.]</ety> <def>A hexagram{1a}, when used as the symbol of Judaism;
called also <altname>Magen David</altname> and <altname>Star of
David</altname>. It is included on the flag of the state of
Israel</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Star of David, Magen David.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moggan</ent>⟦br⟧
